(2617, 304, 'additional_information', 'From the book by Roald Dahl. Dramatized by Richard R. George.\r\n\r\nDirector: Kathleen Rudolph\r\n<h4>Support and Sponsors</h4>\r\nSupport provided by <a href=\"http://www.theproducebox.com/\">The Produce Box</a>.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.theproducebox.com/\"><img class=\"alignnone size-thumbnail wp-image-549\" src=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/the-produce-box-150x150.png\" alt=\"The Produce Box\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>\r\n\r\nOpening weekend sponsored by the <a href=\"http://www.nccoastalpines.org/\">Girl Scouts North Carolina Coastal Pines</a>.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.nccoastalpines.org/http://\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-976\" src=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Girl-Scouts-North-Carolina-Coastal-Pines.png\" alt=\"Logo of the Girl Scouts North Carolina Coastal Pines\" width=\"200\" height=\"91\" /></a>'),
