(3757, 361, 'class_focus', 'This is a nurturing class for young people with developmental and/or physical disabilities. Support staff are welcome to attend.\r\n\r\nWhat happens in a theatre class? Here’s your chance to find out. Have fun as you explore new ways to express yourself, gain confidence, improve social and communication skills and make friends. And take a well-earned bow on the last day of class, as you and fellow classmates share part of your final class with family. In a supportive environment, you will participate in theatre games that help you discover your creativity and then bring stories to life! No previous experience necessary.'),
