(6864, 724, 'event_information', 'Who will be our 2017 Diva? Join us for a cabaret performance full of glitz, glam and giving! Divas! is a competition between some of the fabulous performers who grace the stage of Raleigh Little Theatre. Each performer competes to be the Diva of the Year by raising the most money.\r\n\r\nReception: 7:00 pm\r\nShow: 8:00 pm\r\n\r\nThinking of buying 2 or 4 tickets to the event? <strong>Considering being a sponsor instead</strong>! Sponsorships start at $250 and include tickets to the event. Download the sponsorship form.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;'),
