(6866, 724, 'additional_information', '<h4>This year\'s Divas are:</h4>\r\n<a href=\"https://portal11.bidpal.net/Portal/bpe303915/catalog/item.html?id=1&amp;categoryId=\">Alissa Alba</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://portal11.bidpal.net/Portal/bpe303915/catalog/item.html?id=16&amp;categoryId=\">Jess Barbour</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://portal11.bidpal.net/Portal/bpe303915/catalog/item.html?id=17&amp;categoryId=\">LD Burris</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://portal11.bidpal.net/Portal/bpe303915/catalog/item.html?id=15&amp;categoryId=\">Sarah Griner Duncan</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://portal11.bidpal.net/Portal/bpe303915/catalog/item.html?id=2&amp;categoryId=\">Del Flack</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://portal11.bidpal.net/Portal/bpe303915/catalog/item.html?id=3&amp;categoryId=\">Chris Inhulsen</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://portal11.bidpal.net/Portal/bpe303915/catalog/item.html?id=4&amp;categoryId=\">Lauren Knott</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://portal11.bidpal.net/Portal/bpe303915/catalog/item.html?id=5&amp;categoryId=\">Diana Cameron McQueen</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://portal11.bidpal.net/Portal/bpe303915/catalog/item.html?id=18&amp;categoryId=\">Mason Alexander Park</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://portal11.bidpal.net/Portal/bpe303915/catalog/item.html?id=7&amp;categoryId=\">Emily Spain</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://portal11.bidpal.net/Portal/bpe303915/catalog/item.html?id=8&amp;categoryId=\">Jon Todd</a>\r\n\r\nVisit the <a href=\"http://bidpal.net/divas2017\">Divas! page on BidPal</a> for more information, important updates, or to donate to your favorite Diva!'),
