(9591, 890, 'additional_information', 'Saturday, May 6 (rain date: Sunday, May 7)\r\n11:00am - 6:00pm\r\nRLT’s Raleigh Rose Garden\r\n\r\nSponsored by <a href=\"http://www.witherspoonrose.com/\">Witherspoon Rose Culture</a>. Join us for live demonstrations on gardening techniques by Witherspoon’s rose experts throughout the day.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.witherspoonrose.com/\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-955 size-medium\" title=\"Witherspoon Rose Culture\" src=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Witherspoon-Rose-Culture-black-300x122.png\" alt=\"Witherspoon Rose Culture\" width=\"300\" height=\"122\" /></a>\r\n\r\nAdditional support provided by <a href=\"https://larryscoffee.com/\">Larry\'s Coffee</a>.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://larryscoffee.com/\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-956 size-medium\" title=\"Larry\'s Coffee\" src=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Larrys-Coffee-wide-500px-300x51.png\" alt=\"Larry\'s Coffee logo\" width=\"300\" height=\"51\" /></a>\r\n\r\nInterested in being an exhibiting artist? Application deadline is April 21. Download an <a href=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Art-in-the-Garden-2017-Information.pdf\">Information Sheet</a> and <a href=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Art-in-the-Garden-2017-Artist-Application.pdf\">Artist Application</a> or email <a href=\"mailto:rltartinthegarden@gmail.com\">rltartinthegarden@gmail.com</a>.\r\n\r\nFood trucks include:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"http://mycupoverflowsmobilegrill.com/\">My Cup Overflows</a> (southern soul grill)</li>\r\n 	<li>Fresh Outta Brooklyn (authentic pierogi and kielbasa).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nBe sure to like <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/rltartinthegarden/\">Art in the Garden on Facebook</a>!\r\n\r\nView a <a href=\"http://localhost:8000/visit-us/maps-and-parking/\">map of the area and read parking information</a>.'),
