(9746, 913, 'class_focus', 'Step into the lights and onto the stage as you create and produce a performance of \"Dear Edwina JR!\" Sing and dance to clever, catchy and poignant songs as you follow the adventures of plucky advice-giver-extraordinaire, Edwina Spoonapple. Working with a director, musical director and choreographer, you will create believable characters that act, dance and sing in Edwina’s weekly “Advice-a-Palooza. A bare-bones performance will take place for invited friends and family on the last day of camp. Part of the Cary Academy Summer Program. For rising 7th, 8th and 9th graders.\r\n\r\nNote: This is a two week camp.'),
