(10, 1, '2017-01-23 20:29:42', '2017-01-23 20:29:42', 'This musical comedy is a holiday sugarplum for the whole family; just the right mixture of comedy and romance to add the sparkle of magic to your holiday season. A visually stunning musical combining elegant costumes and scenery with song, dance, conniving step-relatives and resourceful fairy-folk.\\r\\n\\r\\nBased on the fairy tale by Charles Perrault.\\r\\n\\r\\nAdaptation and lyrics by Jim Eiler.\\r\\n\\r\\nMusic by Jim Eiler and Jeanne Bargy.\\r\\n\\r\\nDirected by Rod &amp; Nancy Rich.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>In partnership with WRAL, Friday, December 2 is <a href=\"http://localhost:3000/raleigh-little-theater/shows/cinderella/#\">Coats for the Children night</a> at Cinderella! $10 of every ticket goes to provide warm, winter clothing for Salvation Army families in need.</strong>', 'Cinderella', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'cinderella', '', '', '2017-02-15 11:44:08', '2017-02-15 15:44:08', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/raleigh-little-theater/?post_type=shows&#038;p=10', 0, 'shows', '', 0),
(11, 1, '2017-01-26 17:32:27', '2017-01-26 17:32:27', 'RLT has a <strong>full time staff</strong> of theatre and education professionals. We also contract with a large number of <strong>instructors</strong> to teach our classes and camps year round. And to oversee the operation of the theatre, RLT\'s <strong>board of directors</strong> are committed group of business professionals from our local community. Click a photo to read about each person\'s background and experience.', 'Our People', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'our-staff', '', '', '2017-03-29 16:35:07', '2017-03-29 20:35:07', '', 17, 'http://localhost:8888/raleigh-little-theater/?page_id=11', 0, 'page', '', 0),
