(32, 1, '2017-01-27 17:19:07', '2017-01-27 17:19:07', '<h2>You can help bring the magic of theater to over 40,000 people each year.</h2>\r\n<h3>RLT believes theatre is for everyone to enjoy. Your contributions help keep our ticket costs and class tuition affordable and help us provide scholarships.</h3>\r\nMake a sustaining contribution to support the continued growth and success of Raleigh Little Theatre. Our sustainers support us each month or each quarter.\r\n\r\n<strong><a href=\"https://raleighlittletheatre.secure.force.com/donate/?dfId=a11d0000002KtrFAAS\">BECOME A SUSTAINER</a></strong>\r\n\r\nOr, give a single gift to our annual fund to support Raleigh Little Theatre.\r\n\r\n<strong><a href=\"https://raleighlittletheatre.secure.force.com/donate?dfId=a11d0000001EO9NAAW\" target=\"_blank\">MAKE A DONATION</a></strong>\r\n<h3>RLT Scholarship Fund</h3>\r\nRaleigh Little Theatre is dedicated to providing all young people, regardless of economic status, the opportunity to explore creative possibilities through theatre classes. Help us fulfill this mission by donating to the RLT Scholarship Fund. We need your help to meet the ever increasing demand!\r\n\r\nWrite a check to Raleigh Little Theatre or <a href=\"https://raleighlittletheatre.secure.force.com/donate?dfId=a11d0000001EO9NAAW\">donate online</a>, <strong>designating it for the Scholarship Fund</strong>. Make a difference in a child\'s life.\r\n<h3>Other Ways to Give</h3>\r\n<strong>Give by Phone</strong>\r\n\r\nYou can make a gift by calling (919) 821-4579\r\n\r\n<strong>Give by Mail</strong>\r\n\r\nYou can also give by sending your check to:\r\n\r\nRaleigh Little Theatre\r\n\r\nAttention: Development\r\n\r\n301 Pogue St.\r\n\r\nRaleigh, NC 27607\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<strong>Your contribution is tax deductible</strong>. Raleigh Little Theatre is a non-profit, 501-C(3) tax-exempt organization under the Internal Revenue Code. Donations are tax deductible. Raleigh Little Theatre\'s Federal ID# is 56-0662726.\r\n\r\nRevenue from tickets and class tuition only covers two-thirds of the annual operating costs of the Theatre. Since 1936 Raleigh Little Theatre has provided accessible, affordable theatre productions and award-winning education programs with the help of our community of donors like you.\r\n\r\nFor more information, contact Charles Phaneuf, our Executive Director, at charles@raleighlittletheatre.org or on 919-821-4579 x 221', 'Donate', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'donate', '', '', '2017-02-27 11:56:38', '2017-02-27 15:56:38', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/raleigh-little-theater/?page_id=32', 0, 'page', '', 0),
