(414, 5, '2017-02-24 15:52:43', '2017-02-24 19:52:43', 'Win 2 tickets to see <em><strong>Hamilton, An American Musical</strong></em> in New York City in our Divas! raffle!\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-415 size-medium\" src=\"http://raleighlt.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/HAMILTON-opt-300x125.jpg\" alt=\"hamilton-opt\" width=\"300\" height=\"125\" /></h3>\r\n<h4>The raffle winner will receive:</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Two tickets to see <em>Hamilton</em> in NYC on Saturday 8/19/2017 at 2:00pm</li>\r\n 	<li>Two nights hotel accommodations at the four-star Kimberly Hotel &amp; Suites in NYC, 8/18 - 8/20</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4><a href=\"https://portal11.bidpal.net/Portal/bpe303915/catalog/items.html?itemType=6\">Buy Raffle Tickets</a></h4>\r\n<strong>Are you supporting a particular Diva?</strong> Click the link of the Diva you would like to support or click the \"All Divas\" link to support them all!\r\n\r\nThe drawing will take place at Divas! on March 25, 2017, however you do not need to be present to win.\r\n<h4>Raffle details:</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Hotel accommodations at <a href=\"http://www.kimberlyhotel.com/\">Kimberly Hotel &amp; Suites</a> in New York City</li>\r\n 	<li>Check in: August 18, 2017</li>\r\n 	<li>Check out: August 20, 2017</li>\r\n 	<li><em>Hamilton</em> at the Richard Rodgers Theatre, Saturday, August 19th, 2017 at 2:00 PM</li>\r\n 	<li>Assigned seats: Rear Mezzanine, Row D, Seats 9 &amp; 11 (these seats are next to each other)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\nThis is a fundraising project and all ticket sales benefit Raleigh Little Theatre, a 501(c)3 nonprofit organization. Staff are not eligible to participate in this raffle.', 'Divas! Raffle for Tickets to Hamilton in NYC', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'divas-raffle-for-tickets-to-hamilton-in-nyc', '', '', '2017-03-24 15:18:00', '2017-03-24 19:18:00', '', 0, 'http://raleighlt.wpengine.com/?p=414', 0, 'post', '', 0);
