(495, 3, '2017-02-24 21:54:48', '2017-02-25 01:54:48', 'Vicki Olson has been the Costume Designer at Raleigh Little Theatre for more than 20 years. After receiving her MFA from UNC-G in 1985 she joined RLT as its first professional costume designer. Her creativity and fine work can be seen in countless productions including <em>Spamalot</em>, <em>Hairspray</em>, <em>Hedwig and the Angry Inch</em>, <em>Much Ado About Nothing,</em> and <em>Cinderella</em>.', 'Vicki Olson', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'vicki-olson', '', '', '2017-02-26 22:06:50', '2017-02-27 02:06:50', '', 0, 'http://raleighlt.wpengine.com/?post_type=people&#038;p=495', 21, 'people', '', 0),
(496, 3, '2017-02-24 21:55:03', '2017-02-25 01:55:03', 'Jenny Mitchell is the Associate Costume Designer here at RLT. Her recent Costume Design credits include: <em>The Rivals, The Velveteen Rabbit, Venus in Fur, The Complete Works of Shakespeare (Abridged/Revised), The Rocky Horror Show, The 39 Steps, Sideways Stories from Wayside School, Dear Edwina Jr., Nate the Great, The Miss Firecracker Contest, Merry Christmas Strega Nona, Animal Farm</em> and <em>Junie B. Jones</em>.', 'Jenny Mitchell', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'jenny-mitchell', '', '', '2017-02-26 22:09:41', '2017-02-27 02:09:41', '', 0, 'http://raleighlt.wpengine.com/?post_type=people&#038;p=496', 22, 'people', '', 0),
(497, 3, '2017-02-24 21:55:19', '2017-02-25 01:55:19', 'Duncan Jenner joined Raleigh Little Theatre April 2015, after spending three years separated from the theatre community. He received a Bachelor of Fine Arts from Salem State University in Salem, Massachusetts, and has worked at several theatres in the greater Boston area, including the North Shore Music Theatre, the Wellesley College Theatre, and the Stoneham Theatre. He has also enjoyed working with the young adults of the Boston Children’s Theatre, as well as the opportunity to be a guest lecturer at Salem State University.', 'Duncan Jenner', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'duncan-jenner', '', '', '2017-02-26 22:15:43', '2017-02-27 02:15:43', '', 0, 'http://raleighlt.wpengine.com/?post_type=people&#038;p=497', 45, 'people', '', 0),
