(638, 3, '2017-02-26 11:25:07', '2017-02-26 15:25:07', 'Lee O’Connell moved to Raleigh in 2015 after working in New York as an actor for over five years. She began interning at RLT shortly after her move and transitioned to her current position in 2016. She has spent 15 years working in theatre in various capacities, including performing, producing, stage managing, and education. Lee is a member of the Actors’ Equity Association. A graduate of the University of Virginia, she has additional experience in management, customer service, and independent development experience from producing her own projects.\r\n\r\n919-821-4579 x 230\r\n<a href=\"mailto:lee@raleighlittletheatre.org\">lee@raleighlittletheatre.org</a>', 'Lee O\'Connell', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'lee-oconnell', '', '', '2017-03-10 15:30:49', '2017-03-10 20:30:49', '', 0, 'http://raleighlt.wpengine.com/?post_type=people&#038;p=638', 20, 'people', '', 0),
