(689, 4, '2017-02-27 12:00:13', '2017-02-27 16:00:13', 'The following people have been cast in the Teens on Stage production of Public Works\' <em>The Tempest</em>. Thank you to everyone who auditioned!<!--more-->\r\n\r\nProspero: <strong>Ricky Hall</strong>\r\nAriel: <strong>Sofia Alba</strong> &amp;<strong> Gabriela Alba</strong>\r\nCaliban: <strong>Will Taylor</strong>\r\nMiranda: <strong>Mercedes Ruiz</strong>\r\nFerdinand: <strong>Colton Hartziem</strong>\r\nGonzalo/Ensemble: <strong>Chris Inhulson</strong>\r\nTrinculo/Ensemble: <strong>Emily Miller</strong>\r\nStephano/Ensemble: <strong>Jessica Soffian</strong>\r\nAntonio/Ensemble: <strong>David Snee</strong>\r\nAlonsa/Ensemble: <strong>Angel Koshy</strong>\r\nSebastia/Ensemble: <strong>Sydney Porter</strong>\r\nBoatswain/Ensemble: <strong>Dane Swanser</strong>\r\n\r\nEnsemble:\r\n<strong>Audrey Porter</strong>\r\n<strong>Emma Johnson</strong>\r\n<strong>Isabelle Walsh</strong>\r\n<strong>Alexandra Willbrand</strong>\r\n<strong>Monique Fogg</strong>\r\n<strong>Emily Freer</strong>\r\n<strong>Aidan Morrison</strong>\r\n<strong>Skysha Jones</strong>\r\n\r\nPlease email Patrick Torres, patrick@raleighlittletheatre.org, to indicate acceptance of your role. We will follow up with registration details and a detailed calendar once you have confirmed your participation. Thank you!\r\n\r\nTickets to <em>The Tempest</em> go on sale April 1!', 'Cast list: The Tempest', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'cast-list-the-tempest', '', '', '2017-03-04 14:09:37', '2017-03-04 19:09:37', '', 0, 'http://raleighlt.wpengine.com/?p=689', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(690, 5, '2017-02-26 20:55:43', '2017-02-27 00:55:43', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">RLT has three performance venues on its campus:</span>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Cantey V. Sutton Theatre (298 proscenium theater, completed in 1939)</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Scottie Stephenson Amphitheatre (2,000 outdoor amphitheater, completed 1939) </span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Gaddy-Goodwin Teaching Theatre (up to 150 seat black box theater, completed 1989)</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">For specific seating questions about any venue, please contact the box office at (919) 821-3111 or boxoffice@raleighlittletheatre.org.</span>\r\n<h4>Cantey V. Sutton Theatre</h4>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-728 size-full\" src=\"http://raleighlt.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/MainStageSeatingMap.gif\" width=\"425\" height=\"686\" />\r\n<h4>Gaddy-Goodwin Teaching Theatre</h4>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-729 size-full\" src=\"http://raleighlt.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/gaddy-seating-thrust.gif\" width=\"732\" height=\"688\" />', 'Seating Charts', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'seating-charts', '', '', '2017-02-26 20:55:43', '2017-02-27 00:55:43', '', 15, 'http://raleighlt.wpengine.com/?page_id=690', 0, 'page', '', 0),
