(866, 4, '2017-03-04 16:10:22', '2017-03-04 21:10:22', '<h2>Newsletters</h2>\nSign-up to receive emails from us about what\'s happening in and around the theatre!\n\n<a href=\"https://raleighlittletheatre.secure.force.com/signup/?cfid=a05d0000005AIjrAAG\" target=\"_blank\">Subscribe to Newsletters</a>\n<h2>Follow Us</h2>\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/RLT1936\" target=\"_blank\">Twitter</a> - <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RaleighLittleTheatre\" target=\"_blank\">Facebook</a> - <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/raleighlittletheatre\" target=\"_blank\">Youtube</a>\n<h2>Contact Us</h2>\nIf you have questions, would like to request a brochure, or would like to make a donation, please contact our Business Office.\n<h4>Business Office</h4>\n<ul>\n 	<li><strong>Phone:</strong> 919-821-4579</li>\n 	<li><strong>Fax:</strong> 919-821-7961</li>\n 	<li><strong>E-mail:</strong> info@raleighlittletheatre.org</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Box Office</h4>\n<ul>\n 	<li><a href=\"https://raleighlittletheatre.secure.force.com/ticket/\">Buy tickets online</a></li>\n 	<li><a href=\"http://raleighlt.wpengine.com/visit-us/box-office-hours/\">Box office hours</a></li>\n 	<li><strong>Phone:</strong> 919-821-3111</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Street and Mailing Address</h4>\n301 Pogue Street\nRaleigh, NC 27607\n<h4>Board of Directors</h4>\nTo contact the board, please email <a href=\"mailto:president@raleighlittletheatre.org\">president@raleighlittletheatre.org</a>.\n<h4>Staff</h4>\n<strong>Charles Phaneuf</strong>\nExecutive Director\n919-821-4579 x221\n<a href=\"mailto:charles@raleighlittletheatre.org\">charles@raleighlittletheatre.org</a>\n\n<strong>Patrick Torres</strong>\nArtistic Director\n919-821-4579 x222\n<a href=\"mailto:patrick@raleighlittletheatre.org\">patrick@raleighlittletheatre.org</a>\n\n<strong>Lee O\'Connell</strong>\nDevelopment Coordinator\n919-821-4579 x230\n<a href=\"mailto:lee@raleighlittletheatre.org\">lee@raleighlittletheatre.org</a>\n\n<strong>Meredyth Pederson</strong>\nEducation