(957, 4, '2017-03-27 14:49:34', '2017-03-27 18:49:34', 'At <em>Divas!</em> on Saturday we raised over $57,000 to support RLT’s programs and we had a blast!\r\n\r\nA huge thank you to all of our Divas, donors, the creative team, volunteers, and everyone who helped make the event a big success. Special recognition goes to our winning Diva, <strong>Jess Barbour</strong>, first runner up <strong>Sarah Griner Duncan</strong> and second runner up <strong>Diana Cameron McQueen</strong>. Congratulations to all of our Divas - <strong>Alissa Alba</strong>, <strong>LD Burris</strong>, <strong>Del Flack</strong>, <strong>Chris Inhulsen</strong>, <strong>Lauren Knott</strong>, <strong>Mason Alexander Park</strong>, <strong>Emily Spain</strong>, and <strong>Jon Todd</strong>.\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_958\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"252\"]<a href=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Divas-2017-winner-Jess-Barbour.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-958 size-medium\" title=\"Divas! 2017 winner Jess Barbour\" src=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Divas-2017-winner-Jess-Barbour-252x300.jpg\" alt=\"Divas! 2017 winner Jess Barbour\" width=\"252\" height=\"300\" /></a> Divas! 2017 winner Jess Barbour[/caption]\r\n\r\nThe winner of our <em>Hamilton</em> raffle was Georgia Donaldson. Congratulations!\r\n\r\nThanks again to all! To stay up to date on future Divas news, be sure to follow <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RLTDivas/\">Divas by Raleigh Little Theatre</a> on Facebook.', 'Congratulations to our Divas!', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'congratulations-to-our-divas', '', '', '2017-03-27 14:53:08', '2017-03-27 18:53:08', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8000/?p=957', 0, 'post', '', 0),
