(964, 4, '2017-03-31 21:42:45', '2017-04-01 01:42:45', 'Join Raleigh Little Theatre, <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RaleighBrewingCompany/\">Raleigh Brewing Company</a> &amp; <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hillsboroughstreet/\">Live It Up! On Hillsborough Street</a> this summer for four FREE outdoor movies on Thursdays in July &amp; August! All movies will be held in the Stephenson Amphitheatre next to the Raleigh Rose Garden.<!--more-->\r\n\r\nRSVP on our <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/152131601977245/\">Movies in the Garden Facebook event</a>!\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-965 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Amphitheatre-with-people-setting-up-for-a-movie-e1491010682484.jpg\" alt=\"Amphitheatre with people setting up for a movie\" width=\"1024\" height=\"458\" />\r\n\r\nThe complete list of all four movie titles will be announced on April 24, however, the first of four movies is going to be <a href=\"http://www.imdb.com/title/tt3783958/\"><em>La La Land</em></a> and will be shown on Thursday, July 20.\r\n\r\nThe third &amp; fourth movies in the series will be chosen by audience voting starting on April 3. One poll, selecting from classic movie musicals, will occur on the <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/152131601977245/\">Movies in the Garden Facebook event page</a>. The other poll, selecting from the nominees for the 2017 Academy Award for Best Picture, will be hosted on the <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hillsboroughstreet/\">Live It Up! Hillsborough Street Facebook page</a>.\r\n\r\nMovies in the Garden is a family-friendly event, showing movies that are rated G, PG and PG-13. Concessions (including cold adult beverages provided by Raleigh Brewing) will be available for purchase. Food trucks will be at each show. Please, no outside alcohol, as this is a city park, but feel free to bring cushions/blankets/chairs. Pre-show activities will be held before each movie! Check back for details and mark your calendars now!', 'Movies in the Garden returns this summer!', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'movies-in-the-garden-returns-this-summer', '', '', '2017-04-06 21:31:54', '2017-04-07 01:31:54', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8000/?p=964', 0, 'post', '', 0),
