(966, 7, '2017-04-05 09:39:57', '2017-04-05 13:39:57', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">One of three accredited gardens in the Carolinas, the Raleigh Rose Garden at RLT is the display garden for all new roses presented by the All American Rose Society. The grounds include sixty beds with 56 varieties of roses with hybrid teas, floribundas, grandifloras, miniatures and antiques.</span>\n\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-512 size-large\" src=\"http://raleighlt.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Rose-Garden-007-1024x681.jpg\" alt=\"Rose-Garden-007\" width=\"1024\" height=\"681\" />\n\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The Raleigh Rose Garden can be reserved for special occasions and is an ideal spot for smaller, simpler events. Decorations are unnecessary with the parade of roses that bloom from late May until fall\'s first frost in October or November. Both the fountain and the small stone shelter at either end of the garden make lovely back drops for wedding ceremonies and other gatherings.</span>\n\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If you are looking for a natural setting with little or no extra decoration, the Raleigh Rose Garden is an excellent choice.</span>\n\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-513 size-full\" src=\"http://raleighlt.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Rose-Garden-016-HDR_edit_web.jpg\" alt=\"Rose-Garden-016-HDR_edit_web\" width=\"900\" height=\"599\" />\n\n<strong>We are currently taking reservations for events through to December 31, 2017. Interested in reserving the Rose Garden? Download the <a href=\"http://raleighlt.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Rose-Garden-reservations.pdf\">Rose Garden reservations document</a>. </strong>\n\nFor further information, contact the Special Event Coordinator on Mondays between 9am and noon at Raleigh Little Theatre, 919-821-4579 ext.320 or weddings@raleighlittletheatre.org\n\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-516 size-large\" src=\"http://raleighlt.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Rose-Garden-021-1024x681.jpg\" alt=\"Rose-Garden-021\" width=\"1024\" height=\"681\" />', 'Rose Garden', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '511-autosave-v1', '', '', '2017-04-05 09:39:57', '2017-04-05 13:39:57', '', 511, 'http://localhost:8000/511-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
