(43, 1, '2017-01-27 17:42:21', '2017-01-27 17:42:21', '<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Join us as a member for the 2017-2018 season!</span></h2>\\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Download a</span><a href=\"http://localhost:8000/tickets/RLT-2016-2017-Calendar.pdf\"> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">season calendar and show summary</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> (PDF)</span>\\n\\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Click the links below to order your membership online. You can also order a membership by downloading our</span><a href=\"http://localhost:8000/tickets/RLT-2016-2017-Membership-Form.pdf\"> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">membership order form</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> (PDF) and sending it in.</span>\\n\\n&nbsp;\\n<h3>Sutton Series of classic theatre</h3>\\n<i>All shows presented with Reserved Seating</i>\\n<ul>\\n 	<li><i>Crowns</i> (Gospel Musical)</li>\\n 	<li><i>Little Shop of Horrors</i> (Musical Comedy)</li>\\n 	<li><i>Don’t Dress for Dinner</i> (Comedy)</li>\\n</ul>\\n<h3>City Series of contemporary plays</h3>\\n<i>All shows presented with General Admission</i>\\n<ul>\\n 	<li><i>Perfect Arrangement</i> (Dark Comedy)</li>\\n 	<li><i>What We’re Up Against</i> (Comedy)</li>\\n 	<li><i>Blood Done Sign My Name </i>(Drama)</li>\\n</ul>\\n<h3>Family Series</h3>\\n<ul>\\n 	<li>Grace for President @ NC Museum of History (Musical, General Admission)</li>\\n 	<li>Beanstalk! The Musical (Musical, General Admission)</li>\\n 	<li>Alice @ Wonderland (Musical, Reserved Seating)</li>\\n</ul>\\n<h2>Benefits</h2>\\nBecoming a member is a great way to see shows at RLT! Benefits of being a member include:\\n<ul>\\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Buy your tickets at a lower price than buying them individually</li>\\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Buy your tickets in advance so that you won\'t miss out on the popular show dates</li>\\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Get the best seats available</li>\\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Changing your tickets for a different day is an easy call to the box office and is no charge to you (starting August)</li>\\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\">$6 off tickets to <i>Cinderella</i></li>\\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Support RLT</li>\\n</ul>\\n&nbsp;\\n<h4><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Section Headline: Flex Memberships</span></h4>\\n<b>Flex Memberships</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> are a great way to see shows at RLT. For $68 (including tax) you get three passes. You can use them one at a time or all at once.Suitable for any shows in the 2017-18 season except </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Cinderella.</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> They\'re a great gift idea too! Call the box office on 919-821-3111 to purchase or</span><a href=\"https://raleighlittletheatre.secure.force.com/ticket/#details_a0Sd000000RTQlTEAX\"> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">buy them online</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.</span>\\n\\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Need more information? See our</span><a href=\"http://localhost:8000/shows/16-17/index.html\"> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">season announcement</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> and</span><a href=\"http://localhost:8000/tickets/RLT-2016-2017-Calendar.pdf\"> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">season calendar</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, or call the box office on 919-821-3111 (Mon-Fri noon-5pm)</span>', 'Memberships', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '21-autosave-v1', '', '', '2017-01-27 17:42:21', '2017-01-27 17:42:21', '', 21, 'http://localhost:8888/raleigh-little-theater/2017/01/27/21-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
